description:
As a user of Shopline
  I want ckeck order setting cancel order on
  and shop member login checkout flow
name: check shop order cancel flow detail and Auto revert credit. member/cash

elements.name: check shop order cancel flow detail and Auto revert credit. member/cash

steps.name: I am on Admin Login Page
I fill correct account email to email field
I fill correct account password to password field
I click on login button
I should see successful login
I check intercom message notification frame and click clear intercom message button
I check intercom message notification frame and click intercom message close button
I check new feature alert notification frame and click new feature alert close button
I check and click exclude products panel close button
I check and click no thanks button
I am on Order Setting Page
I check and click cancel order toggle off
I click on 2nd auto cancel order checkbox
I scroll down to update button
I click on update button
I should be redirected to Dashboard Page
I am on Payment Setting Page
I click edit button of payment method list for the same order of row of payment method list included 'Cash on Delivery'
I should be redirected to Payment Edit Page
I fill "(rollback data) Cash on Delivery" to name field
I check and click cancel order toggle off
I click on update button
I should be redirected to Payment Setting Page
I am on Customer List Page
I input email to search field
I should see view button
I click view button for the same order of customer row included 'testuser@shoplineapp.com'
I should be redirected to Customer Detail Page
I click on assign credits button
I should see popover
I fill "13" to amount of credit field
I fill "1" to validity period field
I fill "Testing amount of credits" to reason field
I click on credit save button
I should see row of credit list
I am on Shop Product Index Page
I input "10th Product for Checkout" to search field
1st product of products list should contain '10th Product for Checkout'
